invalid type: string "On January 31, 2026, two incidents were detected involving the domain grossform.ru and the IP address 46.28.69.220, both classified as high risk. The first incident (INC-6140) was related to a cryptomining file, while the second incident (INC-6141) involved an HTTP GET flood. Both incidents indicated malicious activity associated with the same destination IP and domain.˙˙˙˙˙˙